welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Pullach im Isartal, a charming town known for its beautiful views of the Isar River and stunning nature. We invite you to explore our quaint streets, taste delicious Bavarian cuisine, and experience the warm hospitality of our community. Enjoy your stay!"
